lenders.name: Ricki
lenders.loan_because:
What is $25 worth to me?  

It is 11 weeks of buying a tv guide when I can get the information for free on the internet.
It is 7 days of parking tickets when I drive my car to work instead of walking there in 20 minutes.
It is 6 days of buying lunch instead of getting up ten minutes earlier in the morning and making lunch at home to take with me for a fraction of the cost.
It is 2 books when I can borrow them from the library for free.
It is 2 dvds when I have too many already.
It is 1 computer game when I should interact more with people and less with electronics. 
It is 1 take away pizza when I have food in the house that will probably go out of date before it is eaten.
It is 1 month of what I spend on chocolate.


I am lucky, I have a good paying job and little financial commitments.  I can buy the food I want, I live in a secure environment, I have a comfortable home.  I can give up the above luxuries and invest the money in someone who has not had the opportunities, the advantages and  benefits that I have had.

It will not alter my life that much, and it will make me a better, healthier and more sociable person.
